<section class="about-content">
    <div class="about-section">
        <h2>What is CourtNotes?</h2>
        <p>
            CourtNotes is the running commentary of my career - raw notes, honest rants, and practical lessons from
            product design, hackathons, and community leadership. Each post keeps me accountable to building in public
            and opens the door for future collaborators.
        </p>
        <p>
            Expect dispatches on software craft, startup execution, and why Africa-focused products need context-aware
            tooling. If you see an experiment here, it probably shipped in a sprint elsewhere.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-section">
        <h2>Lead, Build, Share</h2>
        <p>
            I lead the Proxyon team on AgriLease while also serving as the Tech Lead for GDG on Campus at my university.
            Coaching peers, running workshops, and refining pitches are as core to my routine as pull requests.
        </p>
        <p>
            Recent projects span React Native (TypeScript), React + Vite, Tailwind CSS, Firebase, and Eleventy. Clean UI,
            scalable architecture, and functionality-first decisions keep every build shippable.
        </p>
    </div>

